devdoc.details: Store and manage voter DIDs on the Apechain blockchain This contract allows authorized parties to register and verify voter DIDs for the KweliVote electronic voting system.

params.nationalId: The national ID to look up

returns._0: The DID associated with the provided national ID

getNationalIdByIndex(uint256).details: Get a voter's national ID by index

getTotalVoters().details: Get the total number of registered voters

returns._0: The total number of registered voters

getVoterDID(string).details: Get a voter's DID by national ID

returns._0: The voter's DID or empty string if not found

isVoterRegistered(string).details: Check if a voter is registered

returns._0: True if voter is registered, false otherwise

params.did: The DID to associate with this voter
params.nationalId: The national ID of the voter

registerVoter(string,string).details: Register a new voter with their DID

transferAdmin(address).details: Transfer admin rights to a new address

params.newAdmin: The address of the new admin

verifyDID(string,string).details: Verify if a DID matches the one stored for a given national ID

returns._0: True if the DID matches, false otherwise
